        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold leading-[1.1] tracking-[-1px] text-white mb-6">Peace Begins With You</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          Whether you donate, volunteer, or simply share our mission, you become part of something bigger than yourself.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/donate" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3.5 bg-white text-primary font-medium text-sm rounded-full btn-pulse-glow shadow-lg shadow-white/20 hover:bg-white/90 transition-all duration-300 min-h-[48px]">
            Donate Now
          </a>
          <a href="/volunteer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3.5 border border-white/40 text-white font-medium text-sm rounded-full glass hover:bg-white/15 hover:border-white/60 transition-all duration-300 min-h-[48px]">
            Volunteer
          </a>
          <a href="/partner" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3.5 border border-white/40 text-white font-medium text-sm rounded-full glass hover:bg-white/15 hover:border-white/60 transition-all duration-300 min-h-[48px]">
            Partner With Us
